{"lemma":"شِدَّةٌ","slug":"شِدَّةٌ","root":"ش.د.د","root_slug":"ش-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-د-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21915"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%90%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَدَّ (šadda)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"intensity","tags":["uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"strength, severity, violence","tags":["uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"misfortune, misery, distress, hardship, discomfort, affliction","tags":["countable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"shadda"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of شَدَّ (šadda).\n\nInstance noun of شَدَّ (šadda, “to geminate”)."},"ipa":["/ʃid.da/","/ʃad.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21915","headword_ar":"شِدَّةٌ","root":"$d","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ad~a","text_ar":"شَدَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb) as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otad~a","text_ar":"اِشْتَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) [and] a subst. from [i. e. syn. with]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otidaAdN","text_ar":"اِشْتِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attribute denoted by the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydN","text_ar":"شَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, MA, L,) in substances and in attributes; (L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firmness, compactness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soundness; strength, power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force; vigour, robustness, sturdiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, L; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ud~N","text_ar":"اَشُدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which, accord. to some, is a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"courage, bravery, firmness of heart:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"niggardliness, tenaciousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avarice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A: [see also 5, last sentence:])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence, violence, intenseness, stress, pressure, severity, strictness, rigour, tightness, straitness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardship, rigour of fortune:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"famine, dearth, want of victuals; hardness, straitness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of subsistence [&c.]: (L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trouble, distress, affliction, calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adversity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, L;) as also [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ud~aY","text_ar":"شُدَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in these as well as in some of the preceding senses, and] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydapN","text_ar":"شَدِيدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [rather meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distressing, event, an affliction,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and rarely used,] of which, (L,) or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, L,) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adaAy^idu","text_ar":"شَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, L,) agreeably with analogy if of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydapN","text_ar":"شَدِيدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but extr. if of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and this pl. also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seditions, discords,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dissensions, whereby men are put into a state of commotion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rigours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pangs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamaraAt","text_ar":"غَمَرَات"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of death: (S and Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmr","text_ar":"غمر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) accord. to Sb, the pl of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$idadN","text_ar":"شِدَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which, he says, preserves its original form [without idghám] because it does not resemble a verb. (L.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAsayotu minohu $id~apF","text_ar":"قَاسَيْتُ مِنْهُ شِدَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I endured, from him, hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from it, hardship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xfotu $ud~aY","text_ar":"خفْتُ شُدَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~atahu","text_ar":"شِدَّتَهُ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1519},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I feared the hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: so says AZ: and he cites this verse:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      faA_in~iY laA A^aliynu liqawoli $ud~aY\n                      \n                     \n                        mina AlHadiydi ↓ \n      walawo kaAnato A^a$ad~a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for, I will not become gentle for a hard saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a saying of hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"though it should be harder than iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbatoniY","text_ar":"اَصَابَتْنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ud~aY","text_ar":"شُدَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hardship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"befell me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AZ, S.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apN","text_ar":"شِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strong, an intense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great, degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any quality &c.]"}],"source_refs":["L","Msb","K","S","A","MA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}